(43, 12, 1, 40, 21, 17, 17, 'Bethany', 'Connection Between Bethany References', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus'' presence in Bethany, highlighting its significance in the narrative. The mention of Bethany in both contexts indicates a continuity in Jesus'' journey leading up to the Passover.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
