(43, 12, 3, 42, 10, 38, 39, 'Mary', 'Connection Between Marys', 'Both passages emphasize the actions of Mary, who is depicted as devoted to Jesus. In John, she anoints His feet, while in Luke, she sits at His feet, highlighting her reverence and commitment.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
